spec_data.Name: perl-Config-IniFiles
spec_data.Description:
Config::IniFiles provides a way to have readable configuration files
outside your Perl script. Configurations can be imported (inherited,
stacked,...), sections can be grouped, and settings can be accessed
from a tied hash.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:20:14 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A module for reading .ini-style configuration files
